These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-1::.
6 different pets are kept: dog, frog, turtle, hedgehog, guinea-pig, lizard
There are 6 different nationalities: american, argentine, indian, mexican, russian, spanish
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
2. the argentine is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
3. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
4. the russian is between the owner of the lizard and the american##2
5. the mexican is between the russian and the argentine##2
6. the american is the owner of the hedgehog##1
7. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the american##1
8. the spanish is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
9. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |       3       |       4        |    5     |   6    |
| Pet           | dog | frog | lizard | guinea-pig | hedgehog    | turtle  |
| Nationality   | spanish | argentine   | mexican       | russian        | american | indian |

