.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-2::.
There are 6 different nationalities: argentine, dutch, german, italian, thai, turkish
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: begonia, poppy, rose, marigold, orchid, daisy
1. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
2. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the thai##1
3. the person who growsmarigold is between the italian and the argentine##2
4. the german is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
5. the argentine is on the far right##1
6. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
7. the italian is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
8. the dutch is on the left of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |  3   |    4    |   5    |     6      |
| Nationality   | dutch | turkish | thai | italian | german | argentine  |
| Flower           | daisy | orchid  | begonia | poppy    | marigold  | rose |

