.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-5::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: disaster, drama, family, satire, sports, western
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: begonia, aconite, rose, daffodil, balloon-flower, dahlia
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
2. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
3. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
4. the person watching drama movies is between the person watching family movies and the person watching sports movies##2
5. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
6. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
7. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
8. the person watching sports movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |   4    |   5   |    6     |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster   | satire    | western | family | drama | sports   |
| Flower         | balloon-flower | begonia | rose | dahlia | daffodil  | aconite |

