.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-6::.
6 different pets are kept: dog, goldfish, frog, lizard, horse, cat
The people have 6 different hobbies: board-games, card-games, dancing, reading, traveling, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the owner of the goldfish##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
6. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
7. the person who's hobby is dancing is the owner of the cat##1
8. the owner of the frog is between the owner of the lizard and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
9. the owner of the dog is the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3    |      4      |     5     |      6      |
| Pet    | dog | cat | horse  | lizard      | frog | goldfish  |
| Hobby   | card-games  | dancing    | reading | board-games | traveling | woodworking |

