.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-7::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: chess, cooking, gardening, hiking, reading, skydiving
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: november, january, february, may, august, june
1. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is hiking##2
4. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person who's birthday is in june##1
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
6. the person who's hobby is reading is between the person who's birthday is in may and the person who's birthday is in august##2
7. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
8. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
9. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |   2    |   3   |    4    |     5     |    6    |
| Hobby       | skydiving | hiking | chess | reading | gardening | cooking |
| Birthday   | february | june    | august  | november    | may    | january    |

