.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-9::.
6 different pets are kept: fish, cat, hamster, frog, mouse, guinea-pig
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: biathlon, sailing, skateboarding, skiing, soccer, surfing
 1. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person who's sport is skiing##1
 2. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the owner of the fish and the person who's sport is surfing##2
 3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far left##1
 4. the person who's sport is skiing is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 5. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 6. the person who's sport is skiing is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 8. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 9. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
10. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |     3      |   4    |   5    |       6       |
| Pet   | fish   | mouse  | cat | frog | guinea-pig | hamster     |
| Sport   | sailing | biathlon | surfing    | soccer | skiing | skateboarding |

