.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-11::.
6 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, frog, hedgehog, rabbit, snake
City: liverpool, boston, venice, san-francisco, hannover, berlin
 1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 2. the owner of the rabbit is the person traveling to hannover##1
 3. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 4. the person traveling to berlin is on the far right##1
 5. the person traveling to hannover is between the person traveling to boston and the owner of the frog##2
 6. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 7. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is the person traveling to liverpool##1
 9. the owner of the cat is between the person traveling to liverpool and the owner of the chinchilla##2
10. the owner of the hedgehog is the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |
| Pet         | snake   | rabbit | frog       | hedgehog | cat    | chinchilla |
| City   | boston | hannover  | venice | liverpool      | san-francisco | berlin        |

