.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-12::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: disco, indie, salsa, hip-hop, pop, soul
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: comedy, family, musical, scientific, sports, time-travel
 1. the fan of salsa is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
 3. the fan of indie is the person watching scientific movies##1
 4. the fan of salsa is between the fan of hip-hop and the person watching time-travel movies##2
 5. the person watching musical movies is between the person watching time-travel movies and the fan of pop##2
 6. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the fan of disco##1
 7. the fan of indie is on the far left##1
 8. the person watching family movies is on the left of the fan of disco##1
 9. the person watching time-travel movies is the fan of disco##1
10. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |         3          |      4      |    5    |      6       |
| Music-Genre           | indie      | hip-hop | salsa | disco   | soul  | pop |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | comedy  | family             | time-travel | musical | sports       |

