.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-13::.
There 6 different types of food: apple, cherry, cranberry, kale, peas, pineapple
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: zinnia, rose, daffodil, lily, poppy, iris
1. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far left##1
2. the person eating apple is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
3. the person who growszinnia is between the person eating peas and the person eating kale##2
4. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
5. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
6. the person who growslily is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
7. the person who growslily is the person eating apple##1
8. the person eating peas is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3   |    4    |     5     |  6   |
| Food          | cranberry | cherry | apple | peas    | pineapple | kale |
| Flower   | daffodil     | iris | lily   | rose | zinnia | poppy |

