 1. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
 2. the security-guard is between the scientist and the person watching zombie movies##2
 3. the scientist is between the person watching western movies and the dancer##2
 4. the photographer is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
 5. the person watching western movies is between the photographer and the person watching documentary movies##2
 6. the person watching epic movies is the paramedic##1
 7. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
 8. the pilot is on the right of the paramedic##1
 9. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
10. the person watching epic movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
