3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who's birthday is in november##2
5. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left##1
7. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
8. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |      3       |   4    |     5      |    6    |
| Birthday   | july   | september   | december        | november   | august        | january   |
| Sport      | biathlon | swimming | snowboarding | skiing | volleyball | cricket |

