.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-20::.
6 different pets are kept: frog, dog, fish, cat, mouse, hamster
There are 6 different nationalities: british, chinese, dutch, italian, russian, turkish
 1. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 2. the british is on the far left##1
 3. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
 4. the italian is the owner of the hamster##1
 5. the owner of the fish is on the far right##1
 6. the turkish is on the right of the italian##1
 7. the chinese is the owner of the fish##1
 8. the russian is on the right of the british##1
 9. the dutch is between the owner of the hamster and the owner of the frog##2
10. the owner of the mouse is the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3      |      4      |       5       |    6    |
| Pet         | cat | frog | dog | hamster | mouse | fish |
| Nationality   | british | russian | dutch      | italian     | turkish       | chinese |

 